  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> perf-3.12.ebuild,
  perf-3.13.1-r1.ebuild, perf-3.15.5.ebuild:
  Drop old Python implementations

  09 Oct 2014; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> perf-3.8-r1.ebuild,
  perf-3.12.ebuild, perf-3.13.1-r1.ebuild, perf-3.15.5.ebuild:
  The libperl ebuild is only a dummy and will be removed; libperl is provided
  by dev-lang/perl.

  18 Jul 2014; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> perf-3.13.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~mips. Bug #517294

